WEBVTT

00:11:29.644 --> 00:11:31.946
Most of us do just fine,

00:11:32.986 --> 00:11:34.695
although it may be hard work,

00:11:35.038 --> 00:11:37.908
and from time to time,
we can do with some advice.

00:11:39.209 --> 00:11:40.480
In that case,

00:11:40.504 --> 00:11:42.527
bear in mind three things.

00:11:43.760 --> 00:11:47.047
Work with advice
that works for your family.

00:11:48.008 --> 00:11:53.486
Remember -- you're the expert,
because you live your family life.

00:11:54.681 --> 00:11:55.965
And finally,

00:11:56.478 --> 00:12:00.468
believe in your abilities
and your creativity,